    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a bit vague lol. like, which side has more weight in the actual empirical data? i've been reading a lot of stuff saying the growth argument is pretty outdated and doesn't actually trickle down like they claim. is that actually the consensus among economists now?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
